---
title: Mediterranean Falafel Sandwich with Tzatziki and Side Salad
description: We're celebrating veggie night with this Mediterranean-inspired sandwich! Packed with pan-fried falafel, creamy hummus, briny pickles, spring mix and tzatziki,  it checks off every flavour box!
